olding%20firm%20Platinum%20Hern%20Private%20Limited%2C%20its%20two%20directors%2C%20CEO%2C%20general%20manager%20and%20a%20store%20in-charge.%20The%20accused%20have%20been%20charged%20with%20cheating%20and%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Scheme%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Torres%20outlets%20opened%20in%20February%20last%20year%20at%20six%20locations%20in%20and%20around%20the%20Maximum%20City.%20They%20sold%20gemstone%20jewellery%20and%20also%20offered%20a%20bonus%20scheme.%20Under%20this%20scheme%2C%20a%20customer%20who%20invested%20Rs%201%20lakh%20would%20get%20a%20pendant%20with%20a%20moissanite%20stone%20worth%20Rs%2010%2C000.%20The%20customers%20have%20now%20realised%20these%20stones%20were%20fake.%20Customers%20were%20promised%206%20per%20cent%20interest%20on%20their%20investment%20to%20be%20paid%20out%20across%2052%20weeks.%20This%20interest%20rate%20climbed%20to%2011%20per%20cent.%20Customers%20said%20they%20got%20some%20payouts%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20but%20they%20stopped%20about%20two%20months%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bumper%20Draw%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20seven%20days%20back%2C%20Torres%20posted%20a%20video%20on%20YouTube%20announcing%20that%20it%20will%20provide%2011%20per%20cent%20interest%20on%20investments%20made%20before%20January%205%2C%20after%20which%20the%20rate%20will%20dip.%20The%20company%20encouraged%20cash%20payments%20by%20offering%200.5%20per%20cent%20extra%20interest.%20The%20move%20aimed%20to%20draw%20a%20flood%20of%20investments.%20On%20January%206%2C%20the%20stores%20were%20shut%20and%20the%20investors%20realised%20they%20had%20been%20scammed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Investors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20these%20investors%20are%20from%20the%20lower%20middle%20class%20and%20include%20vegetable%20sellers%20and%20small%20traders%20who%20were%20lured%20by%20the%20promise%20of%20big%20returns.%20The%20amount%20invested%20under