the%20maximum%20temperature%20settled%20at%2017%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20three%20notches%20below%20the%20season's%20average%2C%20as%20per%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20thick%20layer%20of%20fog%20on%20Saturday%20led%20to%20the%20delay%20of%20at%20least%2045%20trains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECold%20wave%20conditions%20continue%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20north%20India%2C%20including%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20with%20temperatures%20falling%20below%20freezing%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20and%20its%20neighbouring%20cities%20such%20as%20Ghaziabad%20and%20Noida%20received%20rain%20on%20Saturday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMD%20has%20predicted%20a%20generally%20cloudy%20sky%20with%20light%20rain%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20Delhi-NCR%20woke%20up%20to%20dense%20fog%20in%20some%20areas%2C%20which%20led%20to%2045%20trains%20running%20late%2C%20however%2C%20flight%20operations%20at%20Indira%20Gandhi%20International%20Airport%20(IGI)%20remained%20mostly%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20of%20Delhi%2C%20which%20was%20in%20the%20range%20of%20'severe'%20to%20'very%20poor'%20for%20the%20last%20few%20days%2C%20improved%20to%20the%20'poor'%20category%20on%20Sunday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Centre's%20Sameer%20app%2C%20Delhi's%20overall%20AQI%20at%20around%205%20a.m.%20on%20Sunday%20stood%20at%20285.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20AQI%20between%200%20and%2050%20is%20considered%20%26quot%3Bgood%2C%26quot%3B%2051-100%20%26quot%3Bsatisfactory%2C%26quot%3B%20101-200%20%26quot%3Bmoderate%2C%26quot%3B%20201-300%20%26quot%3Bpoor%2C%26quot%3B%20301-400%20%26quot%3Bvery%20poor%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20401-500%20%26quot%3Bsevere%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECold%20wave%20continued%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20with%20the%20local%20meteorological%20department%20predicting%20moderate%20rain%20in%20low-lying%20plains%20and%20snow%20in%20isolated%20a