0the%20box%20office%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftamil%2Fmovies%2Fbox-office%2Fgame-changer-box-office-collection-day-2-ram-charan-and-kiara-advani-starrer-mints-a-whopping-rs-725-crore%2Farticleshow%2F117163729.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pastor%20Who%20Predicted%20Trump's%20Assassination%20Bid%20Now%20Warns%20Of%20A%20Doomsday%20Event%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBrandon%20Dale%20Biggs%2C%20an%20Oklahoma%20pastor%20and%20self-proclaimed%20prophet%20who%20said%20he%20accurately%20predicted%20the%20assassination%20attempt%20on%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20has%20come%20up%20with%20another%20eerie%20prediction.%20Mr%20Biggs%20said%20god%20had%20shown%20him%20a%20vision%20of%20a%2010-magnitude%20earthquake%20which%20may%20kill%20thousands%20of%20people%20across%20the%20US%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2C%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2025%2F01%2F11%2Fprophet-predicted-trumps-assassination-attempt-reveals-new-eerie-vision-22341374%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMetro%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Mr%20Biggs%20claimed%20that%20the%20earthquake%20would%20hit%20the%20New%20Madrid%20fault%20line%2C%20stretching%20through%20Missouri%2C%20Arkansas%2C%20Tennessee%2C%20Kentucky%20and%20Illinois.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'It%20was%20so%20big%2C%20there%20were%201%2C800%20people%20who%20died%20%5Balong%20that%20stretch%5D.%20All%20the%20houses%20on%20cinder%20blocks%20were%20completely%20shaken%20to%20the%20foundation%2C%20they%20just%20fell%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Biggs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'%5BThe%5D%20New%20Madrid%20earthquake%20%5Bis%5D%20so%20big%20%5Band%5D%20when%20it%20happens%20the%20Mississippi%20River%20starts%20it%20goes%20out%20another%20direction.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20in%20a%20YouTube%20video%20dated%20March%2014%2C%202024%2C%20Mr%20Biggs%20said%20the%20US%20president-elect%20would%20be%20targeted%20and%20that%20a%20bullet%20would%20fly%20by%20his%20ear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20Trump%2C%20rising%20up%2C%20and%20then%20I%20saw%20an%20attempt%20on%20his%20life.%20This%20bullet%20flew%20by%20his%20ear%2C%20and%20it%20came%20so%20close%20to%20his%20head%20that%20it%20busted%20his%20eardrum%2C%26quot%3B%20Biggs%20told%20Pastor%20Steve%20Cioccolanti%20in%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20I%20saw%2C%20he%20fell%20to%20his%20knees%20during%20this%20time%20frame%2C%20and%20he%20started%20worshipping%20the%20Lord.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20later%2C%20Mr%20Trump%20narrowly%20survived%20an%20assassination%20attempt%20while%20addressing%20a%20rally%20in%20Butler%20County%2C%20Pennsylvania.%20The%20bullet%20fired%20by%20gunman%20Thomas%20Matthew%20Crooks%20kissed%20Mr%20Trump's%20right%20ear%20before%20the%20security%20officials%20killed%20the%20former.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20a%2010-magnitude%20earthquake%20possible%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20Mr%20Biggs'%20claims%2C%20earthquakes%20of%20magnitude%2010%20or%20greater%20cannot%20happen%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2C%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usgs.gov%2Ffaqs%2Fcan-megaquakes-really-happen-a-magnitude-10-or-larger%5C%22%3EUnited%20States%20Geological%20Survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20(USGS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20magnitude%20of%20an%20earthquake%20is%20related%20to%20the%20length%20of%20the%20fault%20on%20which%20it%20occurs.%20That%20is%2C%20the%20longer%20the%20fault%2C%20the%20larger%20the%20earthquake.%20Currently%2C%20no%20fault%20on%20Earth%20is%20long%20enough%20to%20generate%20such%20a%20megaquake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20largest%20earthquake%20ever%20recorded%20was%20a%20magnitude%209.5%20on%20May%2022%2C%201960%20in%20Chile%20on%20a%20fault%20that%20is%20almost%201%2C000%20miles%2