E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20the%20story%20remained%20the%20same%2C%20even%20if%20the%20details%20changed%3A%20early%20start%2C%20sick%20in%20Virginia%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-game-boy-games-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehours%20lost%20on%20a%20Gameboy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20spending%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20at%20theme%20parks%20before%20heading%20to%20the%20Condo.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22026becab-0ef1-4904-af25-a5c5cba6091d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20felt%20like%20the%20place%20just%20belonged%20to%20us%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20me%2C%20Marco%20Island%20was%20a%20place%20that%20felt%20as%20personal%20as%20someone%20else's%20secret%20family%20recipe.%20It%20was%20a%20place%20only%20for%20us%3A%20nobody%20outside%20our%20family%20had%20ever%20even%20heard%20of%20it.%20A%20small%20retirement%20community%20on%20the%20shores%20of%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%2C%20today%20there%20are%20still%20fewer%20than%2020%2C000%20residents.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20years%20since%20our%20first%20trip%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-us-beach-towns-2017-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMarco%20Island%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20been%20at%20the%20center%20of%20dozens%20of%20core%20memories%3A%20few%20were%20more%20iconic%20than%20splashing%20around%20in%20the%20pool%20as%20thickly-accented%20Bostonian%20snowbirds%20scowled%20their%20way%20through%20calisthenics%20sessions%20at%20us.%20Inevitably%2C%20we%20were%20the%20only%20kids%20in%20the%20complex%20aside%20from%20a%20couple%20of%20others%20who%20were%20visiting%20their%20grandparents%20too%20%E2%80%94%20we'd%20quickly%20make%20and%20forget%20our%20new%20friends%20each%20year%2C%20united%20in%20our%20days'%20long-shared%20experience%20of%20being%20under%20five%20feet%20tall.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECountless%20embarrassing%20photos%20have%20been%20taken%20(and%20hopefully%20lost)%2C%20including%20my%20spot-on%20imitation%20of%20a%20pelican%20loitering%20around%20our%20favorite%20restaurant%2C%20the%20aptly-named%20Pelican%20Bend.%20The%20first%20time%20I%20was%20ever%20allowed%20to%20stay%20up%20until%20midnight%20was%20at%20the%20Condo%20on%20Y2K%2C%20watching%20the%20Nickelodeon%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecoverage%20of%20the%20big%20event.%20Teaching%20my%20younger%20sister%20how%20to%20play%20mini-golf%2C%20taking%20my%20first%20flight%20without%20my%20parents%20when%20I%20visited%20in%20my%2020s.%20I%20even%20introduced%20my%20future%20wife%20on%20a%20video%20call%20to%20my%20grandparents%20while%20I%20was%20staying%20over%20at%20the%20condo%20(%26quot%3BShe's%20a%2010!%26quot%3B%20my%20grandmother%20exclaimed).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f127a6b1-6af7-4933-a488-d062367da819%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20a%20privilege%20to%20have%20that%20time%20with%20my%20family%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20didn't%20know%20it%20then%2C%20but%20each%20early%20morning%20wake-up%20and%20afternoon%20spent%20on%20the%20beach%20was%20a%20privilege%20%E2%80%94%20to%20be%20able%20to%20form%20such%20a%20strong%20connection%20to%20my%20family%2C%20my%20grandparents%2C%20and%2C%20eventually%2C%20my%20love%20of%20travel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20couple%20of%20months%20ago%2C%20my%20parents%20told%20me%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-homeowner-milton-tearing-through-neighborhood-cant-sleep-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHurricane%20Milton%20was%20headed%20straight%20toward%20Marco%20Island%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20we%20held%20our%20collective%20breath%20for%20its%20landfall.%20While%20the%20hurricane%20left%20more%20knocked-over%20lawn%20chairs%20than%20serious%20damage%2C%20we%20were%20all%20r