nary%20at%20this%20difficult%20thing%20all%20the%20time%2C%20no%20matter%20what%2C%20and%20somehow%2C%20there's%20always%20someone%20saying%20we're%20doing%20it%20wrong.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou're%20supposed%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-raise-independent-kids-2017-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eraise%20independent%20kids%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20not%20so%20independent%20that%20they%20feel%20abandoned.%20You%20want%20them%20to%20be%20fully%20themselves%20but%20also%20protect%20them%20from%20a%20world%20that%20isn't%20understanding.%20You%20have%20to%20discipline%20them%2C%20but%20not%20too%20harshly%2C%20or%20you'll%20damage%20them.%20Be%20patient%20but%20not%20permissive.%20Cherish%20every%20moment%2C%20but%20don't%20forget%20to%20think%20about%20and%20prepare%20them%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20have%20to%20balance%20being%20their%20authority%20figure%20and%20their%20empathetic%20listener.%20You%20need%20to%20stay%20calm%2C%20even%20when%20you're%20completely%20exhausted.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floved-company-bored-at-work-found-dream-job-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EYou're%20supposed%20to%20love%20your%20career%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20never%20let%20it%20interfere%20with%20your%20family.%20You're%20supposed%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20every%20opportunity%20but%20also%20don't%20spoil%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20can't%20admit%20how%20hard%20it%20is%20because%20that%20might%20make%20it%20seem%20like%20you%20don't%20love%20them%20enough.%20And%20if%20they%20struggle%20in%20any%20way%20%E2%80%94%20socially%2C%20academically%2C%20emotionally%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20your%20fault.%20Didn't%20you%20read%20the%20right%20parenting%20books%3F%20Take%20the%20right%20classes%3F%20Use%20the%20right%20tone%3F%