n%20an%20interview%20with%20WWF-India%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20%5BBilly%20Arjan%5D%20held%20very%20strong%20views%20and%20would%20regularly%20type%20away%20letters%20on%20his%20trusty%20typewriter%20to%20flag%20his%20concerns%20on%20issues%20that%20he%20considered%20important.%20Though%20his%20prolific%20writing%20was%20curtailed%20due%20to%20the%20physical%20effort%20of%20typing%20in%20his%20last%20years%2C%20even%20with%20failing%20health%2C%20his%20eyes%20would%20light%20up%20at%20the%20mention%20of%20the%20tiger%2C%20and%20he%20was%20always%20eager%20to%20engage%20in%20efforts%20in%20support%20of%20this%20majestic%20animal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinha%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20years%20succeeding%20Billy%20Arjan%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20Dudhwa%20where%20he%20began%20his%20work%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333222%2Fanne-wright-conservationist-wildlife-protection-act-reserves-project-tiger-legacy-raza-kazmi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etiger%20conservation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Those%20years%20were%20coloured%20with%20experiments%20and%20accolades%20%E2%80%94%20navigating%20through%20waves%20of%20conflict%20posed%20by%20communities%20who%20depended%20on%20the%20game%20and%20stepping%20closer%20to%20his%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Bring%20Dudhwa%20under%20Project%20Tiger%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20the%20conservation%20of%20tigers%2C%20Billy%20Arjan%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20breathe%20easy%20until%20he%20had%20pulled%20out%20all%20the%20stops.%20And%20the%20story%20of%20how%20he%20compelled%20Indira%20Gandhi%20to%20consider%20protecting%20the%20forests%20of%20Dudhwa%20puts%20this%20never-die-spirit%20into%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrinda%20tells%20me%20that%20the%20duo%20would%20often%20correspond%20with%20each%20other%20through%20postcards.%20She%20then%20proceeds%20to%20read%20an%20excerpt%20from%20Duff