sion%20in%20the%20local%20markets%2C%20he%20and%20his%20team%20pressed%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20soon%20the%20young%20entrepreneur%20realised%20that%20offering%20higher%20incentives%20to%20farmers%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20enough%20to%20sustain%20long-term%20growth.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20business%20became%20increasingly%20seasonal%2C%20with%20supply%20chain%20challenges%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20maintain%20consistent%20operations.%20So%2C%20we%20had%20to%20stop%20our%20operations%20in%20Uttarakhand%20and%20come%20up%20with%20a%20better%20approach%20to%20expand%20our%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20cold-pressed%20oil%20brand%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20second%20COVID-19%20wave%2C%20he%20and%20his%20team%20noticed%20an%20increasing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328846%2Fsibi-manivannan-runs-gramiya-cold-pressed-oils-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edemand%20for%20cold-pressed%20oils%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20insight%20led%20them%20to%20pivot%20their%20business%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202022%2C%20the%20Heart%20in%20Hills%20team%20ventured%20into%20the%20cold-pressed%20oil%20market%20with%20the%20launch%20of%20Foreka%20in%20Rajasthan.%20This%20expansion%20was%20made%20possible%20by%20the%20support%20Satyam%20received%20in%20November%202020%2C%20when%20he%20was%20awarded%20a%20prestigious%20fellowship%20from%20The%20Buddha%20Institute%2C%20founded%20by%20Ved%20Arya%2C%20an%20alumnus%20of%20IIM%20Ahmedabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Buddha%20Institute%20provided%20us%20with%20a%20generous%20grant%20of%20Rs%2022%20lakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%2C%20which%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20enabling%20the%20team%20to%20scale%20their%20operations.%20Their%20research%20into%20the%20region%20highlighted%20a%20high%20rate%20of%20outmigration%2C%20presenting%20an%20opportunity%20to%20create%20local%20employment.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20exceptional%20quality%20of%20mustard%20seeds%20in%20the%20area%20made%20it%20an%20ideal%20location%20for%20their%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20partnered%20with%20NGOs%20like%20SRIJAN%20to%20establish%20a%20value%20chain%20for%20farming%2C%20offering%20farmers%20better%20prices%20and%20resources%20to%20test%20seed%20quality.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20supporting%20farmers%20directly%2C%20we%20ensured%20fair%20prices%20and%20sustainable%20practices%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Satyam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20breakthrough%20came%20with%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20processing%20unit%20in%20Hindaun%2C%20Karauli%20district%2C%20Rajasthan.%20The%20setup%20includes%20cold-pressed%20machines%20owned%20by%20the%20farmers%2C%20while%20Foreka%20works%20on%20a%20co-profit%20model%2C%20sharing%2050%25%20of%20the%20profits%20after%20covering%20costs.%20Partnering%20with%20two%20Farmer%20Producer%20Organisations%20(FPOs)%2C%20one%20near%20Jhansi%20and%20the%20other%20in%20the%20Chambal%20Valley%2C%20Foreka%20sources%20groundnuts%2C%20processes%20them%2C%20and%20sells%20groundnut%20oil.%20The%20model%20helps%20reduce%20outmigration%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311715%2Fbengaluru-social-impact-startup-mikro-grafeio-creates-employment-in-tier-ii-and-iii-indian-cities%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreate%20local%20employment%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202407px)%20100vw%2C%202407px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222407%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20oil%20processing%20unit%20and%20office%20in%20Hindaun%2C%20Karauli%20district%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0