werful%20example%20of%20love%20and%20persistence.%20After%20enduring%20rejection%2C%20abuse%2C%20and%20the%20heartbreaking%20loss%20of%20her%20partner%2C%20she%20found%20strength%20in%20helping%20others.%20Today%2C%20her%20SIP%20Memorial%20Trust%20provides%20a%20safe%20home%20for%20over%20400%20HIV-positive%20children%2C%20offering%20them%20love%2C%20education%2C%20and%20the%20hope%20of%20a%20brighter%20future.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Mervin%20Preethi%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F390947%2Fnoori-mohammad-abuse-transwoman-hiv-positive-india-children-shelter%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Bihar%20Woman%E2%80%99s%20Mushroom%20Farming%20Business%20Makes%20Rs%202%20Lakh%2FMonth%20%26amp%3B%20Trains%2010000%20Farmers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20faced%20many%20challenges%2C%20but%20I%20never%20let%20them%20deter%20me.%20No%20matter%20how%20tough%20things%20got%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20could%20make%20it%20work.%20I%20just%20had%20to%20keep%20going%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pratibha%20Jha%2C%2040%2C%20whose%20journey%20holds%20true%20the%20statement%20that%20with%20focused%20effort%2C%20anything%20is%20within%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20Muzaffarpur%2C%20Bihar%2C%20a%2010-year-old%20Pratibha%20would%20often%20watch%20local%20farmers%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F380434%2Ftrupti-dhakate-mushroom-farming-sustainable-eco-friendly-women-entrepreneur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultivate%20mushrooms%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20always%20curious%20about%20how%20mushrooms%20grew%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CSomething%20about%20it%20fascinated%20me%2C%20but%20I%20never%20thought%20it%20could%20be%20my%20livelihood%20one%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20life%20took%20a%20sudden%20turn%20when%20he